{"tid":2262920,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"九龍 週六 斯文圍內波  招人","createTime":"2020-10-29T13:01:02.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-22T11:30:30.000Z","uid":103929,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c26b5389ad73456e7df8555bd36552555995598b","tid":2262920,"uid":103929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T13:01:02.000Z","msg":"今次招人係搵一班固定斯文波腳<br />\n<br />\n要求<br />\n1.斯文，懂得（唔係比賽唔使執著）<br />\n2有基本功，樂於組織，團隊精神，球品行先<br />\n（衛生波原因係個嗰要返工，避免受傷）<br />\n<br />\n一直選人試腳，踢走過大量獨食、球品差、脾氣差、潛水嘅人，寧缺毋濫。<br />\n<br />\n目前，群組連續2年每個星期六晚九龍區必踢<br />\n除非暴雨/疫情特發情況<br />\n群組內全部由陌生人開始認識、已經熟絡<br />\n現在均是固定波腳，人品球品甚佳<br />\n（氣氛超級nice！！！！）<br />\n<br />\n年齡層：返工一族<br />\n場地： 7人硬地，夜晚，週六<br />\n（主要長沙灣深水埗樂福黃大仙）近地鐵站<br />\n<br />\n歡迎試腳，合資格才加wts gp<br />\ntelegram：<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/Kaylloo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FKaylloo&d=2u41qa%2Bce9Gslgrzp%2F5Kij4xCSFqVWWaKp6LAuIW5iI%3D&h=5a117ab0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/Kaylloo</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0c32f1f6894fd4d7d0098131a10ca45aa567cd4","tid":2262920,"uid":103929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-06T12:58:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cb03a5551ea4d07f9d83c264408a01c2a96c75e","tid":2262920,"uid":103929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s